title: Qdoba company-owned restaurant sales from 2011 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Sales in million U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 8.
In general Sales in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Sales in million U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2017, and lastly slightly decreasing from 2017 to 2018.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
The highest Sales in million U.S. dollars, of value 436.56 was reached at Year 2017
Minimum Sales in million U.S. dollars about 168.8 was reached at Year 2011
